'''John Fensom''' is an actor and special effects artist who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].

Fensom worked as the additional production assistant for the movie [[Wikipedia:Notting Hill (film)|''Notting Hill'']], which was released in [[1999]], the same year as ''The Phantom Menace''.

He worked on ''Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace'' as an animatronics assistant. He was also the person inside the costume of [[TC-14/Legends|TC-14]], the protocol droid that greeted [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] at the beginning of the movie. He was not the voice of TC-14 however; the droid's voice was provided by actress [[Lindsay Duncan]].

